videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson grabs a rebound and races up the court, bouncing a perfect pass to Manny Bates for an easy jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson threads the needle for NC State slam) 2019/12/19

videos.headline: Johnson threads the needle for NC State slam

videos.description: Samir Doughty puts the game out of reach with a step-back 3 to beat the shot clock, as Auburn pulls away late to beat NC State 79-73.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Doughty drains dagger 3 in Auburn's win over NC State) 2019/12/19
